'''雷纳托·儒尼奥尔·卢兹·桑谢斯'''（{{lang-pt|'''Renato Júnior Luz Sanches'''}}，{{small|{{link-en|Order of Merit (Portugal)|Order of Merit (Portugal)|ComM}}}}，{{bd|1997年|8月18日|catIdx=Sanches, Renato}}），俗称'''雷纳托·桑谢斯'''，是一位司职[[中场|中场]]的[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]][[足球员|足球运动员]]，现時效力[[法国足球甲级联赛|法甲]]球隊[[里爾奧林匹克體育會|里爾]]，并代表[[葡萄牙国家足球队|葡萄牙国家队]]参赛。

==俱乐部生涯==
===早年生涯===
桑谢斯出生在一个贫困的[[圣多美和普林西比|圣多美和普林西比]]－[[佛得角|佛得角]]的[[移民|移民]]家庭<ref>{{cite news|title=Cabo-verdiano Renato Sanches estreou-se no Benfica|url=http://jornaliberal.com/noticias/desporto/2015/10/31/cabo-verdiano-renato-sanches-estreou-se-no-benfica/|access-date=2016-05-10|publisher=Liberal|date=2015-10-31|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160505040601/http://jornaliberal.com/noticias/desporto/2015/10/31/cabo-verdiano-renato-sanches-estreou-se-no-benfica/|archivedate=2016年5月5日|df=}}</ref>，父母在他仅五个月大时便分开，桑谢斯成长于[[里斯本|里斯本]]西北部的问题街区慕斯古埃拉（{{lang|pt|Musgueira}}），即如今{{link-de|卢米亚|Lumiar}}[[堂区_(葡萄牙)|堂区]]的一部分。他的生母，来自佛得角的玛利亚·达斯·多雷斯（{{lang|de|Maria das Dores}}）直到五年后才正式接过抚养权，因他的父亲（同样也被称作雷纳托·桑谢斯）在当时已移居[[法国|法国]]<ref>[http://www.jn.pt/desporto/interior/renato-sanches-registado-quando-tinha-5-anos-5085099.html Renato Sanches registado quando tinha 5 anos] {{Wayback|url=http://www.jn.pt/desporto/interior/renato-sanches-registado-quando-tinha-5-anos-5085099.html |date=20160520010048 }}, jn.pt, vom 19. März 2016 (portugiesisch)</ref>。桑谢斯所在街区曾以骗子著称（{{lang-pt|coração malandro}}，即骗子之心），他在那里也被称为“慕斯古埃拉之饼”<ref>[http://www.record.xl.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/benfica/detalhe/renato-sanches-coracao-malandro.html RENATO SANCHES: CORAÇÃO MALANDRO] {{Wayback|url=http://www.record.xl.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/liga-nos/benfica/detalhe/renato-sanches-coracao-malandro.html |date=20160514194102 }}, record.xl.pt, vom 30. Oktober 2015 (portugiesisch)</ref>。桑谢斯从8岁起开始在慕斯古埃拉雄鹰（{{lang|pt|Águias da Musgueira}}）进行足球训练<ref>{{cite web|last1=Nogueira|first1=Carlos|title=Da Musgueira ao Benfica em 15 minutos|url=http://www.dn.pt/desporto/benfica/interior/da-musgueira-ao-benfica-em-15-minutos-4904397.html|website=dn.pt|publisher=Diário de Notícias|access-date=2016-02-12|date=2015-11-27|archive-date=2016-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160216044751/http://www.dn.pt/desporto/benfica/interior/da-musgueira-ao-benfica-em-15-minutos-4904397.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并在2008年、当他9岁时转投[[本菲卡|本菲卡]]的青训营<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/uefayouthleague/news/newsid=2314984.html|title=UEFA.com's weekly wonderkid: Renato Sanches|last=Pimentel|first=José Nuno|date=2015-12-19|website=UEFA.com|access-date=2016-01-16|archive-date=2015-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222074552/http://www.uefa.com/uefayouthleague/news/newsid=2314984.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。

===本菲卡===
桑谢斯是在[[2014/15球季葡葡牙甲組足球聯賽|2014-15赛季]]，随[[賓菲加體育會B隊|本菲卡B队]]在第二级别的[[葡萄牙足球甲级联赛|葡甲联赛]]完成了自己的职业生涯首秀。他在正式比赛中的首次亮相是2014年10月5日，客场以2比2战平[[費倫斯體育會|費倫斯]]的比赛中首发登场<ref>{{cite news|title=Feirense-Benfica, 2-2: Golo de Fonseca trama águias|url=http://www.record.xl.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/2--liga/detalhe/feirense-benfica-2-2-golo-de-fonseca-trama-aguias-908114.html|access-date=2015-12-13|publisher=Record|date=2014-10-05|archive-date=2021-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210908133143/https://www.record.pt/futebol/futebol-nacional/2--liga/detalhe/feirense-benfica-2-2-golo-de-fonseca-trama-aguias-908114|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一年后，在{{link-de|本菲卡2015至2016赛季|2015–16 S.L. Benfica season|2015-16赛季}}，桑谢斯便从预备队升入一线队，但最初仅是参加训练课程<ref>{{cite news|title=Renato Sanches chega-se à frente|url=http://www.ojogo.pt/Futebol/1a_liga/Benfica/interior.aspx?content_id=4745026|access-date=2015-12-05|work=Record|date=2015-08-25|archive-date=2015-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208232552/http://www.ojogo.pt/Futebol/1a_liga/Benfica/interior.aspx?content_id=4745026|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。他仍然代表预备队参赛，并在2015年8月30日、球队以1比2不敌{{link-en|瓦尔津体育俱乐部|Varzim S.C.}}的比赛中，于开场不到两分钟便先开纪录，射入自己的职业比赛首球<ref>{{cite news|title=All you need to know about new Bayern starlet Renato Sanches|url=http://www.bundesliga.com/en/news/Bundesliga/noblmd34-renato-sanches-all-you-need-to-know-new-bayern-starlet.jsp|accessdate=2016-05-10|publisher=Bundesliga|date=2016-05-10|archive-date=2016-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160511114608/http://www.bundesliga.com/en/news/Bundesliga/noblmd34-renato-sanches-all-you-need-to-know-new-bayern-starlet.jsp|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。17天后，他又在球队以2比3负于[[艾維斯體育會|阿维什]]的比赛中射入两记[[点球|点球]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Renato Sanches bisa|url=http://www.slbenficab.com/desp-aves-3-2-benfica-b-renato-sanches-bisa/|accessdate=2016-05-10|publisher=S.L. Benfica B|date=2015-09-16|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160610153504/http://www.slbenficab.com/desp-aves-3-2-benfica-b-renato-sanches-bisa/|archivedate=2016-06-10}}</ref>。同年10月21日，他还在客场以11比1战胜[[加拉塔萨雷|加拉塔萨雷]]的[[欧洲青年联赛|欧洲青年联赛]]分组赛中取得入球<ref>{{cite news|title=Benfica goleia Galatasaray por 11-1 (sim, leu bem)|url=http://www.maisfutebol.iol.pt/uefa-youth-league/uefa/youth-league-confira-o-onze-do-benfica-b-frente-ao-galatasaray|accessdate=2016-05-10|publisher=Mais Futebol|date=2015-10-21|archive-date=2015-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151224171712/http://www.maisfutebol.iol.pt/uefa-youth-league/uefa/youth-league-confira-o-onze-do-benfica-b-frente-ao-galatasaray|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9天后，桑谢斯终于迎来自己的一线队首秀，在以4比0战胜[[唐迪拉體育會|通德拉]]的比赛中，于第74分钟替换[[莊拿斯·干卡維斯·奧利華拉|莊拿斯]]登场<ref>{{cite news|title=Tondela-Benfica, 0–4 (destaques)|url=http://www.maisfutebol.iol.pt/liga/jonas/tondela-benfica-0-4-destaques|access-date=2015-12-05|work=Mais Futebol|date=2015-10-30|archive-date=2015-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151209023936/http://www.maisfutebol.iol.pt/liga/jonas/tondela-benfica-0-4-destaques|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在2015年11月的国际比赛日后，桑谢斯与本菲卡签订了期至2021年的新合同，并设定了4500万[[欧元|欧元]]的最低解约金条款<ref name=8pres>{{cite news|title=Renato Sanches, a estreia do "8 do presidente"|url=http://www.ojogo.pt/Futebol/1a_liga/Benfica/interior.aspx?content_id=4901688|access-date=2015-12-05|work=O Jogo|date=2015-11-25|archive-date=2015-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208235320/http://www.ojogo.pt/Futebol/1a_liga/Benfica/interior.aspx?content_id=4901688|dead-url=no}}</ref>。11月25日，他首次作为一线队的首发十一人亮相，在客场以2比2战平[[阿斯塔納足球俱樂部|阿斯塔納]]的[[2015–16年欧洲冠军联赛|欧冠联赛]]分组赛中踢满90分钟<ref name=8pres /><ref>{{cite web|title=Benfica fight back to progress and eliminate Astana|url=http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/season=2016/matches/round=2000634/match=2015742/postmatch/report/index.html|website=UEFA.com|access-date=2015-12-05|date=2015011-25|archive-date=2015-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151129065526/http://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/season=2016/matches/round=2000634/match=2015742/postmatch/report/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在接下来的星期一，桑谢斯在客场战胜[[布拉加體育會|布拉加]]的比赛中再度首发出场，而其表现也获得了[[新闻媒体|媒体]]的一致赞赏<ref>{{cite news|title=Renato Sanches? Não joga por eu gostar de jogadores com tranças|url=http://www.maisfutebol.iol.pt/rui-vitoria/liga/renato-sanches-nao-joga-por-eu-gostar-de-jogadores-com-trancas|access-date=2015-12-05|work=Mais Futebol|date=2015-11-30|archive-date=2015-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151203230449/http://www.maisfutebol.iol.pt/rui-vitoria/liga/renato-sanches-nao-joga-por-eu-gostar-de-jogadores-com-trancas|dead-url=no}}</ref>。12月4日，年仅18岁的桑谢斯射入了代表本菲卡一线队的首个入球，他在以3比0战胜[[科英布拉大學足球會|科英布拉大學]]的比赛中<ref>{{cite news|title=Renato Sanches colocou a cereja no bolo de Jonas|url=http://desporto.sapo.pt/futebol/primeira_liga/artigo/2015/12/05/analise-benfica-3-0-academica|access-date=2015-12-05|work=Record|date=2015-12-05|archive-date=2015-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151206181039/http://desporto.sapo.pt/futebol/primeira_liga/artigo/2015/12/05/analise-benfica-3-0-academica|dead-url=no}}</ref>，距离对方球门30米开外以一记劲射首开纪录，从而成为本菲卡自21世纪以来，在其主场[[光明球场|光明球场]]取得入球的最年轻球员<ref>{{cite news|date=2015-12-05|title=Renato Sanches é o mais novo do século a marcar na Luz|url=http://desporto.sapo.pt/futebol/primeira_liga/artigo/2015/12/05/renato-sanches-e-o-mais-jovem-do-seculo-a-estrear-se-a-marcar-no-estadio-da-luz|website=SAPO Desporto|access-date=2016-03-19|archive-date=2016-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160302175155/http://desporto.sapo.pt/futebol/primeira_liga/artigo/2015/12/05/renato-sanches-e-o-mais-jovem-do-seculo-a-estrear-se-a-marcar-no-estadio-da-luz|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而这个入球也被评选为当月最佳入球<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.abola.pt/nnh/ver.aspx?id=593338|title=Renato Sanches vence prémio para o melhor golo de dezembro|date=2016-01-19|publisher=SJPF|access-date=2016-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160403045530/http://www.abola.pt/nnh/ver.aspx?id=593338|archive-date=2016-04-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 。

桑谢斯的第2个联赛入球发生于2016年1月2日，在对阵[[維多利亞體育會|甘馬雷斯]]的比赛中射入全场唯一入球<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.maisfutebol.iol.pt/liga/02-01-2016/v-guimaraes-benfica-0-1-destaques|title=V. Guimarães-Benfica, 0–1 (destaques)|last=Ferreira|first=Bruno José|date=2016-01-02|publisher=Maisfutebol|access-date=2016-01-16|archive-date=2016-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160106024238/http://www.maisfutebol.iol.pt/liga/02-01-2016/v-guimaraes-benfica-0-1-destaques|dead-url=no}}</ref>。4月24日，当本菲卡在客场以1比0战胜[[里奧艾維足球俱樂部|里奧艾維]]的比赛结束后，他成为了对方一些[[种族主义|种族主义]]球迷的挑衅对象，他们发出[[猴子|猴子]]的声音。而桑谢斯则报以微笑并模仿猴子挥动手臂作为回应<ref>{{cite news |last=Perez |first=Nathalia |date=2016-04-25 |title=Diante do racismo de alguns torcedores do Rio Ave, Renato Sanches reagiu com um sorriso |url=http://trivela.uol.com.br/diante-do-racismo-de-alguns-torcedores-do-rio-ave-renato-sanches-do-benfica-reagiu-com-um-sorriso/ |website=Trivela |access-date=2016-05-10 |archive-date=2016-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160430073310/http://trivela.uol.com.br/diante-do-racismo-de-alguns-torcedores-do-rio-ave-renato-sanches-do-benfica-reagiu-com-um-sorriso/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。5月8日，在球队以2比0战胜[[馬里迪莫體育會|馬里迪莫]]的比赛中，桑谢斯于上半场累计两张[[黄牌|黄牌]]被罚离场，从而错过本菲卡在该赛季的最后一场联赛<ref>{{cite news|title=Benfica on track for record 35th title after victory|url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/sport/benfica-on-track-for-reco/2768218.html|accessdate=2016-05-10|publisher=Channel News Asia|date=2016-05-09|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160510085144/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/sport/benfica-on-track-for-reco/2768218.html|archivedate=2016-05-10}}</ref>。

===拜仁慕尼黑===
2016年5月10日，桑谢斯以3500万欧元的转会费<ref>{{cite news|date=2016-05-10|title=Bayern sign Portugal starlet Renato Sanches|url=http://www.fcbayern.de/en/news/news/2016/fc-bayern-sign-renato-sanches-100516.php|website=FC Bayern Munich|access-date=2016-05-10|archive-date=2016-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160510132335/http://www.fcbayern.de/en/news/news/2016/fc-bayern-sign-renato-sanches-100516.php|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，与[[德甲|德甲]]俱乐部[[拜仁慕尼黑|拜仁慕尼黑]]签订了一份自7月1日起生效、为期五年的合同，这笔交易总额高达8000万欧元，附加的4500万欧元取决于其所取得的成就<ref>{{cite web|url=http://web3.cmvm.pt/SDI/emitentes/docs/FR60211.pdf|title=Comunicado|date=2016-05-10|website=CMVM|publisher=S.L. Benfica|format=PDF|access-date=2016-05-10|archive-date=2016-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160510131331/http://web3.cmvm.pt/SDI/emitentes/docs/FR60211.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Crawford|first=Stephen|date=2016-05-10|title=Bayern Munich confirm Renato Sanches signing|url=http://www.goal.com/en/news/11/transfer-zone/2016/05/10/23333552/official-bayern-munich-confirm-renato-sanches-signing-for|website=Goal.com|access-date=2016-05-11|archive-date=2016-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160511132655/http://www.goal.com/en/news/11/transfer-zone/2016/05/10/23333552/official-bayern-munich-confirm-renato-sanches-signing-for|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这笔交易也使得桑谢斯成为离开本土联赛的最昂贵[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]球员<ref name=caro>{{cite news|date=2016-05-10|title=Renato Sanches é o português mais caro a sair da Liga|url=http://www.maisfutebol.iol.pt/transferencias/benfica/renato-sanches-e-o-portugues-mais-caro-a-sair-da-liga|website=Maisfutebol|access-date=2016-05-10|archive-date=2016-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160510150151/http://www.maisfutebol.iol.pt/transferencias/benfica/renato-sanches-e-o-portugues-mais-caro-a-sair-da-liga|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{refn|三位前记录保持者均是以3000万欧元的价格售出：[[里卡多·卡瓦略|卡瓦略]]于2004年从[[波尔图足球俱乐部|波尔图]]至[[切尔西足球俱乐部|切尔西]]，[[佩佩|佩佩]]于2007年从波尔图至[[皇家马德里|皇家马德里]]，以及[[法比奧·干查奧|干查奧]]于2011年从本菲卡至皇家马德里。<ref name=caro/>|group=注}}，以及首位加盟拜仁慕尼黑的葡萄牙球员<ref name=jogar>{{cite news|date=2016-05-10|title=Renato Sanches é o primeiro português a jogar no Bayern Munique|url=http://www.maisfutebol.iol.pt/benfica/transferencias/renato-sanches-e-o-primeiro-portugues-a-jogar-no-bayern-munique|website=Maisfutebol|access-date=2016-05-10|archive-date=2016-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160510184105/http://www.maisfutebol.iol.pt/benfica/transferencias/renato-sanches-e-o-primeiro-portugues-a-jogar-no-bayern-munique|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而是项加盟费也是拜仁历史上第四高的转会支出，仅次于[[哈维·马丁内斯|哈维·马丁内斯]]、[[马里奥·格策|马里奥·格策]]和[[阿图罗·比达尔|阿图罗·比达尔]]<ref name=jogar/>。

