==国家队生涯==
[[File:1_renato_sanches_2016.jpg|thumb]]对阵[[波兰国家足球队|波兰]]的比赛中射入扳平比分一球]]
桑谢斯曾代表各青年组别的[[葡萄牙国家足球队|葡萄牙国家足球队]]共出场40次<ref>{{cite web|title=Renato Sanches at FPF|url=http://www.fpf.pt/Selecoes/Futebol/Masculino/Selecao-Sub-19/Jogadores/Jogador/Id/792107/SoccerType/11/RENATO-SANCHES|website=Federação Portuguesa de Futebol|access-date=2015-12-05|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208192131/http://www.fpf.pt/Selecoes/Futebol/Masculino/Selecao-Sub-19/Jogadores/Jogador/Id/792107/SoccerType/11/RENATO-SANCHES|archivedate=2015-12-08}}</ref>。其中他随{{link-de|葡萄牙17岁以下国家足球队|Portugal national under-17 football team|葡萄牙U17队}}参加了{{link-de|2014年欧洲U-17足球锦标赛|2014 UEFA European Under-17 Championship}}，并帮助球队进军半决赛，但不敌最终的冠军[[英格蘭17歲以下足球代表隊|英格兰]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Europeu de sub-17: Benfica domina convocatória|url=http://maisfutebol.iol.pt/sub-17-europeu-sub-17-benfica-fc-porto-sporting-selecao/535844e90cf20e3c592cedf7.html|access-date=2014-10-05|work=Maisfutebol|date=2014-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006125236/http://maisfutebol.iol.pt/sub-17-europeu-sub-17-benfica-fc-porto-sporting-selecao/535844e90cf20e3c592cedf7.html|archive-date=2014-10-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2016年3月18日，桑谢斯被[[費爾南多·桑托斯_(葡萄牙)|桑托斯]]征召入成年组国家队以备战对阵[[保加利亞國家足球隊|保加利亚]]和[[比利时国家足球队|比利时]]的两场[[友谊赛|友谊赛]]<ref>{{cite news|date=2016-03-18|title=Estreia de Renato Sanches e vários regressos nos convocados de Portugal|url=http://pt.uefa.com/uefaeuro/news/newsid=2344789.html|website=UEFA|access-date=2016-03-19|archive-date=2016-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402084812/http://pt.uefa.com/uefaeuro/news/newsid=2344789.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。他在葡萄牙于[[莱里亚|莱里亚]]以0比1不敌保加利亚的比赛中完成成年组首秀，于第76分钟替换[[威廉·卡維奴|威廉·卡維奴]]登场，并在不久后受到一位侵入场内的球迷的问候<ref>{{cite news |date=2016-03-25 |title=Jovem invadiu o relvado para... abraçar Renato Sanches |url=http://www.record.xl.pt/multimedia/fotogalerias/detalhe/jovem-invadiu-o-relvado-para-abracar-renato-sanches.html |newspaper=Record |access-date=2016-03-30 |archive-date=2016-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160327235307/http://www.record.xl.pt/multimedia/fotogalerias/detalhe/jovem-invadiu-o-relvado-para-abracar-renato-sanches.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

桑谢斯入选了葡萄牙征战[[2016年欧洲足球锦标赛|2016年欧洲足球锦标赛]]的大名单，这使他成为被选入国际大赛的最年轻的葡萄牙人，打破了[[基斯坦奴·朗拿度|基斯坦奴·朗拿度]]在十二年前保持的纪录<ref>{{cite news|title=Portugal's Sanches breaks Ronaldo's national call-up record|url=http://www.business-standard.com/article/news-ians/portugal-s-sanches-breaks-ronaldo-s-national-call-up-record-116051801507_1.html|accessdate=2016-05-20|publisher=Business Standard|date=2016-05-18|archive-date=2016-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160519191059/http://www.business-standard.com/article/news-ians/portugal-s-sanches-breaks-ronaldo-s-national-call-up-record-116051801507_1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[圣艾蒂安|圣艾蒂安]]对阵[[冰岛国家足球队|冰岛]]的[[2016年欧洲足球锦标赛决赛圈F组#葡萄牙_v._冰岛|球队揭幕战]]中，桑谢斯完成了正式国际比赛首秀，在1比1战平的最后19分钟替换[[若昂·穆蒂尼奥|若昂·穆蒂尼奥]]亮相<ref>{{cite news|last=Dillon|first=John N.|title=Renato Sanches impressed in his Euro 2016 debut for Portugal|url=http://www.bavarianfootballworks.com/2016/6/14/11937838/renato-sanches-debut-portugal-iceland-euro-2016|accessdate=2016-06-14|publisher=Bavarian Football Works|date=2016-06-14|archive-date=2016-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160618072515/http://www.bavarianfootballworks.com/2016/6/14/11937838/renato-sanches-debut-portugal-iceland-euro-2016|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。而在6月25日依靠加时赛以1比0战胜克罗地亚的八分之一决赛中，他促成了全场唯一的入球，并当选为{{link-de|比赛最佳球员|Man of the match|本场最佳球员}}<ref>{{cite news|last=Atkin|first=John|date=2016-06-25|title=Quaresma snatches extra-time win for Portugal|publisher=UEFA|access-date=2016-06-26|url=http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/season=2016/matches/round=2000744/match=2017998/postmatch/report/|archive-date=2016-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160626134341/http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/season=2016/matches/round=2000744/match=2017998/postmatch/report/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。观察到这样的表现，前国脚{{link-de|安东尼奥·索萨|António Sousa}}指出“当他拿球时你不会注意到他有多年轻。无论身体还是精神上，他都准备充分”，而主教练桑托斯则赞扬桑谢斯为对压力免疫球员<ref name="pais">{{cite news|last=Quixano|first=Jordi|title=Renato Sanches, un jugador de barrio para Portugal|url=http://deportes.elpais.com/deportes/2016/06/29/actualidad/1467208694_667948.html?rel=cx_articulo#cxrecs_s|accessdate=2016-06-30|work=El País|date=2016-06-29|archive-date=2016-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160814074556/http://deportes.elpais.com/deportes/2016/06/29/actualidad/1467208694_667948.html?rel=cx_articulo#cxrecs_s|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 。五天后，在对阵波兰的四分之一决赛中，桑谢斯刷新了此前由罗纳尔多所保持的国际大赛最年轻首发葡萄牙球员纪录<ref name="including">{{cite news|last=Darwin|first=Stephen|title=Renato Sanches breaks two records at Euro 2016... Including one of Ronaldo's!|url=http://www.goal.com/euro2016/en/article/renato-sanches-breaks-two-records-at-euro-2016-including-one-of-ronaldos/cu8tbe01e1op1cqt2mlns0n36|accessdate=2016-06-30|publisher=Goal.com|date=2016-06-30|archive-date=2016-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160703030914/http://www.goal.com/euro2016/en/article/renato-sanches-breaks-two-records-at-euro-2016-including-one-of-ronaldos/cu8tbe01e1op1cqt2mlns0n36|dead-url=no}}</ref>。经过上半场与[[蘭尼|蘭尼]]的撞墙配合后，他在禁区外的一脚劲射扳平比分，成为欧锦赛史上淘汰赛阶段的最年轻入球者以及所有阶段的第三年轻入球者<ref name="including"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/news/newsid=2386610.html|title=Renato Sanches becomes third-youngest EURO scorer|publisher=UEFA|date=2016-06-30|accessdate=2016-07-01|archive-date=2016-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701174346/http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/news/newsid=2386610.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。继120分钟内战成1比1，桑谢斯又在[[点球大战|点球大战]]中代表葡萄牙第二个登场并一蹴而就，进而再度当选本场最佳球员<ref>{{cite news|title=Poland 1–1 Portugal|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/36603665|accessdate=2016-06-30|publisher=BBC Sport|date=2016-06-30|archive-date=2016-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629203747/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/36603665|dead-url=no}}</ref>。赛后他的队友纳尼和[[何塞·馮特|何塞·馮特]]称赞了桑谢斯的耐力、信心和向长辈学习的欲望<ref name="hytner">{{cite news|last=Hytner|first=David|title=Manchester United may rue missing out on Renato Sanches, says Nani|url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2016/jul/01/manchester-united-rue-missing-renato-sanches-euro-2016|accessdate=2016-07-04|work=The Guardian|date=2016-07-01|archive-date=2016-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701235122/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2016/jul/01/manchester-united-rue-missing-renato-sanches-euro-2016|dead-url=no}}</ref>。当葡萄牙于决赛依靠加时赛以1比0战胜东道主法国队后，桑谢斯因其出色的表现而被评为赛事最佳新秀<ref name="young-player">{{cite web |url=http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/news/newsid=2389937.html |title=Renato Sanches named Young Player of the Tournament |quote=New European champion Renato Sanches has been chosen above Kingsley Coman and Portugal team-mate Raphael Guerreiro for the SOCAR Young Player of the Tournament award. |date=10 July 2016 |website=UEFA.com |publisher=Union of European Football Associations |accessdate=2016-07-11 |archive-date=2016-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160711141137/http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/news/newsid=2389937.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

